      <heading>Tue May 28 (Jasurin)    :: &amp;gRe&amp;n: &amp;gQuests and Roleplay&amp;n</heading>
      <slot>4</slot>
      <level>203</level>
      <author>0</author>
      <date>0</date>
      <text>First, let me say, &quot;Thank you Radnor&quot;.  Ideas like that are exactly why
I nagged Masema into putting in this board, for which we all owe him a
brief round of applause.  I'm currently trying to put together a series
of short quests on a few different plotlines, but in the meantime, I'd
love to continue to hear more ideas like Radnor's.  Even more than that
sort of list of ideas, though, I would love to have people come to this
board or to simply come directly to me with ideas for personal roleplay
activities.  Take the time to look at your roleplay and ask questions
like, &quot;How could this be better with an Imm's help?  What if we could get
someone to run some NPCs to oppose our plans?  Perhaps we could find a
way to involve the general public in our roleplay for a session or two?&quot;
If you come up with any ideas whatsoever, *please* give other people the
chance to help you bring them to fruition - really good roleplay tends
to come from the cooperation of multiple parties, where the unexpected
can create situations that would never happen while simply roleplaying
within one's own little clique.

-&amp;gJasurin&amp;n
</text>
