      <heading>Tue Jun  4 (Jasurin)    :: &amp;gOffer&amp;n</heading>
      <slot>8</slot>
      <level>203</level>
      <author>0</author>
      <date>0</date>
      <text>Mudmail me your character's name, his guild status, and some form of his
or her background(as short or as long as you'd like), and a brief summary
of where they are and what they are doing right now.
Describe to me the sort of roleplay you most enjoy, being as specific or
as vague as you would like.  I will look over the above information and
keep an eye out for you online.  If and when I see you, and I have the
time or inclination, I will offer to run roleplay for you starting from
wherever you are and whatever you're doing at that precise IC moment.  If
you're in an Inn's common room, or currently travelling between cities,
or literally anywhere else, I'll run you your own private roleplay quest.
Mind you, this is entirely at my own discretion, but it gives you a rare
chance to experience totally unplanned roleplay, which may be virtually
anything you can imagine(or rather I can imagine) tailored to what I know
about your character and your roleplay preferences.
But if you don't &amp;gsend&amp;n me anything, I can't &amp;grun&amp;n anything for you.  So get
on it, people!

-&amp;gJasurin&amp;n
</text>
